name: "Shut Your Eyes And You'll Burst Into Flames" (Lino print)
description:
Inspired by David Lynch's "Twin Peaks" and the legendary log lady..

Printed by hand with brown ink on tan-coloured Winsor & Newton paper and signed and numbered in graphite.
Extremely limited edition of 20. Each measures approx 12x8 inches (measurements will vary slightly from print to print), and since they're handprinted each print is unique.
